    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Threading tools, many-toothed or with a single cut edge, shaped especially for cutting or finishing external or internal threads; usually used in conjunction with a lathe.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
